Privacy
If you have questions or want to make a complaint about us processing your personal data, or about our Privacy Policy, we encourage you to get in touch via email.
Got questions?
If you have any questions about our
Privacy Policy
or about our processing of your personal data, you’re welcome to contact our Privacy Team via email at
privacy@trustpilot.com
and we’ll do our best to help!
Where to direct complaints
You also have the option of raising a complaint with the
Danish Data Protection Agency
, which is the lead supervisory authority regarding our platform.
You can find contact information for the Danish Data Protection Agency here:
www.datatilsynet.dk
.
Any complaints to the Danish Data Protection Agency should specify the name of the company concerned, the alleged privacy violation, your contact information, and whether or not you'd like the particulars of your complaint shared with Trustpilot.
